item.title: Something from the Cellar: Hollywood Hopes
item.description:
Tinseltown is the promised land for so many of the actors, musicians and presenters we’ve had on the show over the last four and a half years. But for these three, those dreams have turned into a scarcely believable reality!


Hannah Waddingham and Luke Evans talk to us about how they got their big breaks through a timely combination of luck and talent, while singer Aled Jones reminds us that the journey to the top isn’t always smooth... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/acaaaf98-69c1-4a94-b843-5ea7e3892f66
